data.description:
Tired of apartment living? Pull up to the front door in a spacious driveway. Wash and dry your clothes in your own private laundry room in. Have a privately fenced in yard and patio for your children or pets to play. Have plenty of room for growing your own garden. This home is conveniently located, East Fort Lauderdale Duplex near Federal Hwy, Holy Cross, 1.6 miles from Lauderdale by the Sea, and 3.7 miles from FXE. New A/C 2021
First/Last/Security required.
Email or text to schedule a call or viewing

First/last month and security deposit required. Water, sewage, trash included. Teanant is responsible for electric and yard maintenance. Will consider one year or short term lease agreement.
